Title: Set minReadySeconds for node-collectors
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: helm
Date: 1649073049
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 1.0.0-alpha.2

The Pods of node-collector-container-metrics and node-collector-machine-sections sometimes report
being ready for a short amount of time before failing. With this werk, the Pods will no longer
become available if a failure occurs.
